msgid "rubber-hose cryptanalysis"
msgstr "rubber-hose cryptanalysis"

#: ../../R/rubber-hose-cryptanalysis.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../R/rubber-hose-cryptanalysis.rst:9
msgid ""
"[sci.crypt newsgroup] The technique of breaking a code or cipher by finding "
"someone who has the key and applying a rubber hose vigorously and repeatedly"
" to the soles of that luckless person's feet until the key is discovered. "
"Shorthand for any method of coercion: the originator of the term drily noted"
" that it \"can take a surprisingly short time and is quite computationally "
"inexpensive\" relative to other cryptanalysis methods. Compare :ref:`social-"
"engineering`\\, :ref:`brute-force`\\."
msgstr ""
"[sci.cryptニュースグループ] "
"鍵を持っている誰かを見つけ、その不運な人の足の裏にゴムホースを精力的かつ繰り返し当てて鍵が判明するまで続けることによって、コードや暗号を破る技術。あらゆる強制の手段を表す省略表現。この語の発案者は、それが他の暗号解読手法に比べて「驚くほど短時間で済み、計算コストもかなり安い」と素っ気なく述べた。\\"
" :ref:`social-engineering`\\ 、\\ :ref:`brute-force`\\ と比較せよ。"
